      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Distinct weak layers exist in the old snowpack. This applies especially on west, north and east facing slopes. The snowpack remains generally prone to triggering. <br/> Outgoing longwave radiation during the night was reduced over a wide area. The snowpack will be moist at low and intermediate altitudes. <br/> Some snow fell on Wednesday over a wide area."
